{{else if (ne rustWebFramework "none")}}
This is a Rust **{{rustWebFramework}}** service. Add a handler function and mount it on the router, mirroring the existing routes.
{{else if (ne javaWebFramework "none")}}
This is a Java **{{javaWebFramework}}** service. Add a controller/handler and map it to a route following the existing endpoints.
{{else if (ne elixirWebFramework "none")}}
